@node HELP_MOUSE "AmigaGuide® Help: Mouse"
@{b}Mouse@{ub}
The common-or-garden mouse, also known as mus musculus, is a small rodential
mammal. It is usually greyish in color, sometimes even black or white. The
mouse feeds on grain, cheese and delicacies such as sweets. It can be very
cute if used as a pet, but to farmers it is usually an irritating pest.
@endnode

